quran[82]{c,v,t}:
  100,9,Ese ntazi ko hari igihe abari mu mva bazazurwa
  100,10,N’ibiri mu bituza (by’abantu) bigashyirwa ahagaragara
  100,11,"Mu by’ukuri, uwo munsi Nyagasani wabo azaba azi neza ibyabo"
  101,1,Ikizahonda (umunsi w’imperuka)
  101,2,Ikizahonda ni iki
  101,3,Ni iki kizakumenyesha ikizahonda
  101,4,"Ni umunsi (w’imperuka), ubwo abantu bazamera nk’ibinyugunyugu binyanyagiye"
  101,5,N’imisozi ikamera nk’ipamba ritumuka
  101,6,"Bityo, uwo umunzani we (w’ibikorwa byiza) uzaremera (bikaruta ibibi)"
  101,7,Azaba mu buzima bw’umunezero (Ijuru)
  101,8,Ariko uwo umunzani we (w’ibikorwa byiza) uzaba utaremereye (bikarutwa n’ibibi)
  101,9,Ubuturo bwe buzaba ari mu muriro witwa Hawiya
  101,10,Ni iki cyawukumenyesha (umuriro wa Hawiya)
  101,11,Ni umuriro ugurumana bikabije
  102,1,Mwarangajwe no gushaka kwigwizaho ubutunzi
  102,2,Kugeza ubwo mugeze mu mva
  102,3,Oya ntibikwiye! Bidatinze muzamenya (ko ubuzima bw’imperuka ari bwo bwiza kuri mwe)
  102,4,Oya nanone! Bidatinze muzamenya
  102,5,"Oya! Iyo muza kugira ubumenyi budashidikanywaho (bw’ibijyanye n’iherezo ryo kurangazwa no kwigwizaho imitungo, ntimwari guhugira mu by’isi)"
  102,6,"Mu by’ukuri, muzabona umuriro wa Jahanamu"
  102,7,Rwose muzawibonera imbonankubone
  102,8,"Kandi rwose, kuri uwo munsi muzabazwa ku ngabire (mwahawe muri ku isi)"
  103,1,Ndahiriye ku gihe
  103,2,"Mu by’ukuri, umuntu ari mu gihombo"
  103,3,"Uretse abemeye bagakora ibikorwa byiza, bakagirana inama z’ukuri kandi bakanagirana inama zo kwihangana"
  104,1,"Ibihano bikomeye bizaba kuri buri wese unegura abandi, usebanya"
  104,2,Urundanya imitungo agahora ayibara
  104,3,Yibwira ko umutungo we uzatuma abaho ubuziraherezo
  104,4,"Oya! Mu by’ukuri, azajugunywa mu muriro witwa Hutwama (ushwanyaguza)"
  104,5,Ni iki kizakumenyesha Hutwama
  104,6,Ni umuriro wa Allah ucanye
  104,7,(Uwo muriro) uzajya uzamuka ugere ku mitima (y’abazaba bawurimo)
  104,8,"Mu by’ukuri, bazaba bawufungiwemo"
  104,9,(Baziritse) ku nkingi ndende (kugira ngo batawusohokamo)
  105,1,Ese (yewe Muhamadi) ntiwamenye uko Nyagasani wawe yagize abagabye igitero bari ku nzovu (baje gusenya ingoro ya al Kaabat iri i Maka)
  105,2,Ese umugambi wabo mubisha ntiyawuburijemo
  105,3,Nuko akaboherereza uruhuri rw’inyoni
  105,4,Zikabatera amabuye y’ibumba yatuye
  105,5,Maze akabagira nk’ibyatsi byakanjakanjwe
  106,1,Kubera imibanire y’aba Quraish (mu mujyi wabo)
  106,2,No kubera ingendo zabo (z’ubucuruzi) zo mu gihe cy’ubukonje no mu cy’impeshyi (batekanye)
  106,3,"Bityo, nibagaragire (Allah) Nyagasani nyir’iyi ngoro (Al Ka’aba)"
  106,4,"(We) wabagaburiye mu gihe cy’amapfa, ndetse akanabaha umutekano mu gihe cy’ubwoba"
  107,1,Ese wamenye uhinyura umunsi w’ibihembo
  107,2,Uwo ni wa wundi uhutaza imfubyi
  107,3,Ntanashishikarize (abandi) kugaburira abakene
  107,4,"Bityo, ibihano bikomeye biri ku basenga"
  107,5,Babandi birengagiza amasengesho yabo (ntibayakorere ku bihe byayo byagenwe)
  107,6,Babandi bakora ibyiza bagamije kwiyerekana
  107,7,Kandi bakanga (gutiza) ibikoresho byo mu rugo (ku babikeneye)
  108,1,"Mu by’ukuri, (yewe Muhamadi) twaguhaye (ibyiza byinshi birimo) umugezi wo mu Ijuru witwa Kawthar"
  108,2,"Bityo, ujye usenga unatange ibitambo kubera Nyagasani wawe"
  108,3,"Mu by’ukuri, ukwanga ni we nyakamwe (ntazigera abona ibyiza haba ku isi ndetse no ku mperuka)"
  109,1,"Vuga (yewe Muhamadi) uti \"Yemwe bahakanyi"
  109,2,Sinsenga ibyo musenga
  109,3,Kandi na mwe ntimusenga uwo nsenga
  109,4,Ndetse nanjye sinzigera nsenga ibyo musenga
  109,5,Kandi namwe ntimuzigera musenga uwo nsenga
  109,6,"Mufite idini ryanyu, nanjye nkagira idini ryanjye"
  110,1,"Igihe ubutabazi bwa Allah (kuri wowe Muhamadi) buzaza, ndetse n’intsinzi (yo kubohora umujyi wa Maka)"
  110,2,Nuko ukabona abantu binjira mu idini rya Allah ku bwinshi
  110,3,"Uzasingize ikuzo rya Nyagasani wawe, unamusabe imbabazi; kuko ari we Uwakira ukwicuza (kw’abagaragu be)"
  111,1,"Amaboko yombi ya Abu Lahab147 arakorama (kubera ko yayakoreshaga abangamira Intumwa y’Imana), ndetse na we ubwe azorama"
  111,2,Umutungo we n’urubyaro rwe ntacyo bizamumarira
  111,3,Azinjira mu muriro ugurumana
  111,4,Ndetse n’umugore we watwaraga ibiti (by’amahwa yajyaga atega mu nzira Intumwa y’Imana yanyuragamo)
  111,5,Mu ijosi rye (uwo mugore) hazaba hari umurunga wo mu muriro
  112,1,"Vuga (yewe Muhamadi) uti \"We ni Allah, umwe Rukumbi"
  112,2,"Allah, Uwishingikirizwa"
  112,3,Ntiyabyaye kandi ntiyanabyawe
  112,4,Ndetse nta na kimwe ahwanye na cyo
  113,1,"Vuga (yewe Muhamadi) uti \"Nikinze kuri (Allah), Nyagasani w’igitondo"
  113,2,Ngo andinde inabi y’ibyo yaremye
  113,3,Anandinde ikibi cyo mu ijoro ryijimye igihe riguye
  113,4,Anandinde ikibi cy’abarozikazi bahuha ku mapfundo
  113,5,Ndetse anandinde inabi y’umunyeshyari igihe arigize
  114,1,"Vuga (yewe Muhamadi) uti \"Nikinze kuri (Allah), Nyagasani w’abantu"
  114,2,Umwami w’abantu
  114,3,Imana y’abantu
  114,4,"Ngo andinde ububi bwa (shitani) yoshya gukora ibibi, nyuma ikabireka (igihe umuntu yibutse Allah)"
  114,5,Yoshya imitima y’abantu gukora ibibi
  114,6,Yaba (shitani) yo mu majini cyangwa mu bantu